=09=09=09=09Euro-area inflation rose to 3.4% in the year to May, significan=
tly above the=20
European Central Bank=01,s 2% ceiling. America=01,s consumer-price inflatio=
n hit=20
3.6%. The ECB left interest rates unchanged.
